html.p:
The Create Training Plan
template contains the necessary components to create a detailed training plan, which you can then implement and track.

Use this template to determine training topics, establish a training team, identify the groups that need training and budge allotted, document training materials, and gather training feedback questions.

ul.li: Before you begin adding content, explore the template by expanding each branch to become familiar with the different elements of the Create Training Plan template.
Add Progress icons to track your progress.

html.p: When you are ready to create your training plan, add your content by inserting new subtopics, or by editing existing topics.
